WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:11.530 --> 00:00:16.040
Congratulations on passing the 
Hellhorde Promotion Exam.

3
00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:23.320
You've gone from Hyper Cadet Harm-Marshal 
to Awesome Great Cadet Inquisitor.

4
00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:26.510
That's my daughter for you.

5
00:00:24.370 --> 00:00:28.710
Hell-Lord's Daughter
Awesome Great Cadet Inquisitor
    Maomao-chan

6
00:00:26.510 --> 00:00:28.750
Thank you very much, Papa.

7
00:00:28.750 --> 00:00:30.850
I mean, Your Majesty.

8
00:00:30.850 --> 00:00:32.890
I will give you a reward.

9
00:00:32.890 --> 00:00:34.340
Whatever you want.

10
00:00:34.340 --> 00:00:36.530
A magic crystal skeleton?

11
00:00:36.530 --> 00:00:38.160
An evil dragon fang?

12
00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:40.570
Or perhaps a hydra scale?

13
00:00:40.890 --> 00:00:43.180
State your wish.

14
00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:45.660
In that case...

15
00:00:48.110 --> 00:00:48.970
I...

16
00:00:49.890 --> 00:00:53.030
I want a piggyback ride...

17
00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:54.520
What?!

18
00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.760
I know you're the Hell-Lord,

19
00:00:56.760 --> 00:01:02.110
and appearances are important, 
so I held back all this time...

20
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:07.030
But deep down, I want 
piggyback rides and stuff.

21
00:01:08.020 --> 00:01:08.760
Ah!

22
00:01:08.760 --> 00:01:11.070
No, I'm sorry!

23
00:01:11.070 --> 00:01:12.600
I was asking for too much.

24
00:01:12.810 --> 00:01:14.790
Of course!

25
00:01:14.790 --> 00:01:15.810
Eh?

26
00:01:15.810 --> 00:01:18.640
I had been concerned about 
appearances, too...

27
00:01:18.910 --> 00:01:22.000
but you know I'd love to 
give you a piggyback ride!

28
00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:23.920
Papa!

29
00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.280
Okay!

30
00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:30.530
You can ride piggyback as much as you want!

31
00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:51.500
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

32
00:03:05.870 --> 00:03:07.730
I'm so high up!

33
00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:12.250
I can almost reach the ceiling!

34
00:03:13.070 --> 00:03:15.140
You sure are tall, Papa!

35
00:03:15.140 --> 00:03:18.600
But right now, you're even 
taller, Maomao-chan.

36
00:03:18.850 --> 00:03:21.600
Does that make me the tallest in the world?!

37
00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:22.620
Geh-heh-heh.

38
00:03:22.620 --> 00:03:24.540
Make sure you hold on tight.

39
00:03:24.540 --> 00:03:27.950
Watch out for the pointy bits of my horns.

40
00:03:27.950 --> 00:03:29.320
'Kay!

41
00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:31.550
Yay!

42
00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:37.730
Thank you very much, Papa.

43
00:03:37.730 --> 00:03:39.200
I had fun.

44
00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:40.400
Me too.

45
00:03:40.900 --> 00:03:42.760
That was nice.

46
00:03:42.760 --> 00:03:47.070
Letting loose instead of holding 
yourself back, that is.

47
00:03:47.970 --> 00:03:50.090
Until now, to keep up appearances,

48
00:03:50.090 --> 00:03:55.090
I watched quietly in the back with my 
arms folded at concerts.

49
00:03:55.530 --> 00:04:00.580
Starting next time, I'll go 
a bit closer to the front!

50
00:04:00.580 --> 00:04:02.000
Geh-heh-heh...

51
00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:03.560
That's for the best, Papa!

52
00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.810
By the way, daughter of mine.

53
00:04:05.810 --> 00:04:09.210
Earlier, you said, "piggyback 
rides and stuff."

54
00:04:09.210 --> 00:04:11.880
It sounds like there's more that you desire.

55
00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:12.750
Huh?

56
00:04:12.750 --> 00:04:13.690
I couldn't...

57
00:04:13.950 --> 00:04:15.450
It's fine by me!

58
00:04:15.450 --> 00:04:16.780
Tell me what you want!

59
00:04:18.070 --> 00:04:19.530
Then...

60
00:04:20.430 --> 00:04:21.730
Playing house.

61
00:04:21.730 --> 00:04:23.320
Mama!

62
00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:24.500
Food!

63
00:04:24.500 --> 00:04:27.780
I'm hungry, Mama!

64
00:04:27.780 --> 00:04:30.990
Okay, it'll be ready in no time!

65
00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:35.040
Geh-heh-heh...

66
00:04:36.510 --> 00:04:38.550
Next up, a horsey ride!

67
00:04:38.550 --> 00:04:40.560
Neigh!

68
00:04:40.560 --> 00:04:42.280
Clip-clop, clip-clop...

69
00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:42.980
Go, go!

70
00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:43.870
Neigh!

71
00:04:43.870 --> 00:04:46.930
Welcome to my blue underground lake house!

72
00:04:47.270 --> 00:04:48.690
Right this way.

73
00:04:48.690 --> 00:04:49.970
Geh-heh-heh.

74
00:04:49.970 --> 00:04:51.940
Thank you for inviting me over.

75
00:04:51.940 --> 00:04:54.320
Hellvanian Families!

76
00:04:55.990 --> 00:04:58.760
Also, also...

77
00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:00.750
There's still more?

78
00:05:00.750 --> 00:05:03.840
You truly are the Hell-Lord's daughter.

79
00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:05.970
Your desires are endless!

80
00:05:05.970 --> 00:05:07.300
Geh-heh-heh!

81
00:05:07.300 --> 00:05:08.180
Is that bad?

82
00:05:08.870 --> 00:05:12.080
It's been so long since we 
played together, Papa...

83
00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:13.470
It's fine by me!

84
00:05:13.470 --> 00:05:14.840
I am the Hell-Lord!

85
00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:17.340
All desires are mine for the taking!

86
00:05:17.340 --> 00:05:22.680
I will devour every last craving you have!

87
00:05:21.710 --> 00:05:23.540
Yay!

88
00:06:05.430 --> 00:06:06.910
Go on.

89
00:06:11.330 --> 00:06:12.340
Whoa there.

90
00:06:58.350 --> 00:07:01.350
The Hell-Lord and
Maomao-chan
played together

91
00:07:03.990 --> 00:07:05.020
Ah!

92
00:07:05.020 --> 00:07:06.500
Your Majesty!

93
00:07:07.250 --> 00:07:09.870
Where have you been?

94
00:07:09.870 --> 00:07:12.290
As for the secret that 
Torture found out today...

95
00:07:12.290 --> 00:07:13.170
Shh.

96
00:07:13.730 --> 00:07:15.830
I'm retiring for the night.

97
00:07:19.060 --> 00:07:20.160
As you wish.

98
00:07:31.300 --> 00:07:33.840
Papa, do your best at work

99
00:07:40.810 --> 00:07:43.600
Picture Diary

100
00:07:40.810 --> 00:07:43.600
Unruled
Notebook

101
00:07:40.810 --> 00:07:43.600
Torture

102
00:07:47.570 --> 00:07:51.280
The Royal
Empire's
password that
the Hell-Lord
previously lost

103
00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:55.280
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

104
00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:55.280
I love Papa

105
00:07:51.990 --> 00:07:53.900
I love Papa!

106
00:07:56.290 --> 00:07:57.550
Bell Mall.

107
00:07:58.140 --> 00:07:59.580
Leaf.

108
00:07:59.580 --> 00:08:00.660
Fukudaya.

109
00:08:00.890 --> 00:08:01.910
Ashcan.

110
00:08:01.910 --> 00:08:02.630
Ah!

111
00:08:02.630 --> 00:08:04.770
I ended my word with an N!

112
00:08:04.770 --> 00:08:06.020
I'm impressed, Your Highness.

113
00:08:06.020 --> 00:08:07.600
You're even strong at shiritori!

114
00:08:07.600 --> 00:08:09.110
What a wide vocabulary you have.

115
00:08:09.890 --> 00:08:12.050
Who do you think you're dealing with here?

116
00:08:13.570 --> 00:08:17.550
Thanks to the advanced education I received 
from the royal family's exclusive tutors,

117
00:08:17.550 --> 00:08:20.420
I happen to possess an extensive vocabulary.

118
00:08:20.420 --> 00:08:23.110
Winning at shiritori is as easy as pie!

119
00:08:23.110 --> 00:08:24.910
No, as easy as torture!

120
00:08:24.910 --> 00:08:26.470
Wow, Your Highness!

121
00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:32.080
But now that you mention it,
it's almost time for your torture.

122
00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:34.400
Is it really okay to be relaxing like this?

123
00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:36.110
It's fine, it's fine.

124
00:08:36.380 --> 00:08:38.850
I'm sure the torture 
won't be anything scary.

125
00:08:38.850 --> 00:08:40.780
The jig is up if you admit that part.

126
00:08:52.900 --> 00:08:54.730
Apologies for the wait.

127
00:08:58.150 --> 00:08:59.080
Wha—?!

128
00:09:08.670 --> 00:09:11.960
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

129
00:09:13.170 --> 00:09:15.270
She's brought out the big guns!

130
00:09:15.630 --> 00:09:17.070
A hot iron...

131
00:09:17.070 --> 00:09:20.010
Looks like the Hellhorde's 
not playing around anymore.

132
00:09:23.510 --> 00:09:27.630
However, you've faced death many 
times only to come out on top.

133
00:09:27.910 --> 00:09:29.760
It'll take more than that!

134
00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.700
Isn't that right, Your Highness?

135
00:09:31.700 --> 00:09:32.990
You betcha!

136
00:09:32.990 --> 00:09:34.590
You're shaking like a leaf!

137
00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:37.120
Are you okay, Your Highness?

138
00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:41.170
Could it be that your fortitude has weakened 
from your prolonged imprisonment?

139
00:09:41.170 --> 00:09:43.210
You can't be serious, Ex.

140
00:09:43.210 --> 00:09:47.060
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

141
00:09:47.060 --> 00:09:49.450
Have faith in me!

142
00:09:49.450 --> 00:09:52.310
Your words sound promising, but 
not with that look on your face!

143
00:09:52.610 --> 00:09:54.770
Now, Princess.

144
00:09:54.770 --> 00:09:57.210
Today's torture will be...

145
00:10:00.710 --> 00:10:02.530
Raclette cheese!

146
00:10:02.370 --> 00:10:03.950
Moo

147
00:10:04.340 --> 00:10:06.980
I'll use this iron to heat up the cheese,

148
00:10:06.980 --> 00:10:10.210
so that it can be enjoyed in 
a melty and delicious state.

149
00:10:13.010 --> 00:10:15.540
What a relief!

150
00:10:14.560 --> 00:10:15.540
Your Highness?!

151
00:10:15.540 --> 00:10:18.780
I'm so... I'm so relieved...

152
00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.650
I thought I was going to die...

153
00:10:22.510 --> 00:10:25.960
Your Highness, the torture hasn't begun yet.

154
00:10:27.370 --> 00:10:29.890
After being faced with the 
terror of that hot iron,

155
00:10:29.890 --> 00:10:32.150
I can easily hold out against that cheese.

156
00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:46.750
It looks so good!

157
00:10:46.020 --> 00:10:47.530
She easily crumbled in no time!

158
00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.470
Cheese!

159
00:10:50.470 --> 00:10:51.980
Cheese!

160
00:10:52.870 --> 00:10:56.890
I bet it's amazing!

161
00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:57.290
So much for that vocabulary 
from an advanced education.

162
00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:04.110
The cheese!

163
00:11:04.110 --> 00:11:06.000
The cheese is oozing down!

164
00:11:07.590 --> 00:11:10.360
Where are you going, cheese?!

165
00:11:15.340 --> 00:11:18.280
Cheesy-cheesy yum-yum!

166
00:11:17.400 --> 00:11:20.260
Has your brain melted 
away, vocabulary and all?

167
00:11:22.070 --> 00:11:24.530
The princess
confessed

168
00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:37.230
Delish!

169
00:11:40.570 --> 00:11:43.270
"Cheese and Kabao share 
the same voice actor."

170
00:11:44.010 --> 00:11:47.000
His Majesty wasn't satisfied 
with today's secret, either.

171
00:11:47.890 --> 00:11:50.840
It's true that His Majesty is 
a big fan of voice actors.

172
00:11:50.840 --> 00:11:53.310
I wouldn't be surprised if he knew already.

173
00:11:54.970 --> 00:11:57.110
Which means for tomorrow...

174
00:11:57.110 --> 00:11:57.830
Ah.

175
00:11:58.320 --> 00:11:59.540
That's right.

176
00:11:59.540 --> 00:12:03.200
I can't torture her tomorrow.

177
00:12:04.630 --> 00:12:06.200
Cheese...

178
00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:11.960
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

179
00:12:16.190 --> 00:12:19.950
'Tis time for your routine 
physical, Princess.

180
00:12:20.900 --> 00:12:22.600
Routine physical?

181
00:12:22.600 --> 00:12:23.550
Yes.

182
00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:26.790
It'll soon be one month since 
the princess was captured.

183
00:12:27.450 --> 00:12:30.670
In order to lead a healthy 
life in captivity,

184
00:12:30.670 --> 00:12:35.370
the Hellhorde conducts monthly 
health check-ups on all prisoners.

185
00:12:35.370 --> 00:12:37.230
Now <i>that's</i> an unexpected benefit.

186
00:12:37.840 --> 00:12:41.560
And so, I shan't be torturing you today.

187
00:12:41.560 --> 00:12:44.050
I'll be administering a 
routine physical instead.

188
00:12:44.050 --> 00:12:46.460
Routine... physical...

189
00:12:46.460 --> 00:12:48.920
Oh, does that go for that big guy as well?

190
00:12:48.920 --> 00:12:49.650
Indeed.

191
00:12:51.340 --> 00:12:55.440
Datarma has his check-up as well, 
which is why I'm by myself today.

192
00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:59.470
Now, to begin, I'll be drawing your blood.

193
00:12:59.470 --> 00:13:00.450
I'll talk.

194
00:13:00.450 --> 00:13:01.290
What?!

195
00:13:01.290 --> 00:13:03.990
Wh-Wh-What's wrong, Your Highness?

196
00:13:01.290 --> 00:13:09.790
I'll talk... So please spare me...

197
00:13:03.990 --> 00:13:06.270
You're not being tortured today.

198
00:13:06.680 --> 00:13:09.790
Wait, are you scared of needles?

199
00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:10.880
Eep!

200
00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:12.040
C'mon!

201
00:13:12.040 --> 00:13:14.850
There's no way I'd be scared of needles!

202
00:13:14.850 --> 00:13:17.770
I just happened to almost 
confess out of habit!

203
00:13:17.600 --> 00:13:20.190
Confess out of habit?

204
00:13:18.760 --> 00:13:20.190
Confess out of habit?

205
00:13:21.550 --> 00:13:23.170
That's right.

206
00:13:23.170 --> 00:13:25.210
Your Highness may be royalty,

207
00:13:25.210 --> 00:13:27.380
but you were always at the very 
front on the battlefield,

208
00:13:27.380 --> 00:13:29.130
receiving the most wounds in battle.

209
00:13:30.190 --> 00:13:33.980
You even reached the position of Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

210
00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:36.860
You couldn't possibly be scared of needles!

211
00:13:36.860 --> 00:13:39.140
Of course not, Ex!

212
00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:42.340
Sharps Container

213
00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:42.340
Rubbing Alcohol

214
00:13:44.090 --> 00:13:45.880
Rubbing Alcohol

215
00:13:48.270 --> 00:13:51.380
Now then, Princess, let's get started...

216
00:13:52.760 --> 00:13:53.760
Your Highness?!

217
00:13:56.620 --> 00:13:59.520
You were so calm on the battlefield, 
receiving wound after wound...

218
00:13:59.520 --> 00:14:00.720
I mean, c'mon!

219
00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:01.990
C'mon!

220
00:14:02.950 --> 00:14:04.190
Whoops...

221
00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:06.780
Whoops...

222
00:14:04.190 --> 00:14:06.900
You're fine when you cut your 
finger on paper by accident...

223
00:14:06.900 --> 00:14:08.000
Cut your finger.

224
00:14:07.990 --> 00:14:11.910
Eek

225
00:14:08.440 --> 00:14:11.910
But it's scary if someone tells you, 
"Cut your finger with paper right now!"

226
00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:13.690
First things first!

227
00:14:13.690 --> 00:14:15.420
Do you even know your way around a needle?!

228
00:14:16.700 --> 00:14:22.290
How do I know you won't mess up trying 
to find a vein and make a huge mess?!

229
00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:23.770
I'll be fine.

230
00:14:24.130 --> 00:14:26.910
I used to work as a nurse.

231
00:14:26.910 --> 00:14:28.040
What?!

232
00:14:28.560 --> 00:14:31.710
Incidentally, this uniform is the 
one I used to wear back then.

233
00:14:32.200 --> 00:14:33.930
So please, rest assured.

234
00:14:34.770 --> 00:14:36.400
Oh, I know.

235
00:14:36.400 --> 00:14:38.000
What if I defected?

236
00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:38.980
And joined the Hellhorde.

237
00:14:38.980 --> 00:14:40.070
Your Highness?!

238
00:14:40.070 --> 00:14:44.540
No! No needles!

239
00:14:42.350 --> 00:14:44.840
Not a scrap of shame, decency, or dignity.

240
00:14:44.540 --> 00:14:47.070
I'm scared of pain!

241
00:14:45.280 --> 00:14:47.070
Let me think.

242
00:14:47.500 --> 00:14:50.900
I'm not here to try and 
hurt the princess, either.

243
00:14:52.700 --> 00:14:56.450
Anesthetic Tape

244
00:14:53.150 --> 00:14:56.450
I do have this local anesthetic patch.

245
00:14:57.070 --> 00:15:00.460
I can use this to make the needle painless.

246
00:15:00.460 --> 00:15:04.120
But if I go to the trouble of using 
it, I'd want a secret in exchange...

247
00:15:04.630 --> 00:15:07.500
The royal treasures are hidden in a 
room on the east side of the castle!

248
00:15:07.500 --> 00:15:08.470
That was instant!

249
00:15:13.430 --> 00:15:15.000
Tell me when you're gonna poke me!

250
00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:15.790
Promise!

251
00:15:15.790 --> 00:15:17.770
No taking me by surprise!

252
00:15:17.770 --> 00:15:20.670
I'll spank you if you do that!

253
00:15:19.070 --> 00:15:20.930
There, all done!

254
00:15:23.550 --> 00:15:26.480
You were really brave, so 
you get a bear sticker.

255
00:15:28.130 --> 00:15:29.910
It didn't hurt!

256
00:15:29.910 --> 00:15:31.960
Hooray for modern medicine!

257
00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:39.710
The princess was
in good health

258
00:15:40.870 --> 00:15:42.150
I see.

259
00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:45.210
The royal treasures are in 
a room on the east side.

260
00:15:45.210 --> 00:15:47.010
What do you think?

261
00:15:47.010 --> 00:15:48.160
Geh-heh-heh.

262
00:15:48.500 --> 00:15:51.900
I'd feel bad if we stole 
their royal treasures.

263
00:15:52.430 --> 00:15:56.430
'Tis Time for
"Torture," Princess

264
00:16:01.170 --> 00:16:02.540
Your Highness.

265
00:16:02.540 --> 00:16:05.100
I apologize for being unable 
to save you last time.

266
00:16:05.740 --> 00:16:10.790
I was so focused on my spell that I 
didn't notice I had let go of you.

267
00:16:11.810 --> 00:16:15.060
This time, with my newly-acquired spell,

268
00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:20.190
I, Louch Brittan, the White Knight, 
will be sure to save you!

269
00:16:21.010 --> 00:16:23.610
Please wait for me, Your Highness!

270
00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:37.880
Your Highness.

271
00:16:38.660 --> 00:16:39.710
Your Highness.

272
00:16:41.010 --> 00:16:42.070
Your Highness.

273
00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:44.680
It's been quite some time.

274
00:16:44.680 --> 00:16:48.990
Louch Brittan, White Knight 
of the Imperial First Legion,

275
00:16:47.440 --> 00:16:51.820
Imperial
First
Legion

276
00:16:47.940 --> 00:16:51.820
Louch
Brittan

277
00:16:48.990 --> 00:16:51.830
has arrived to fetch Your 
Highness once again.

278
00:16:52.230 --> 00:16:56.010
I'm sorry for letting my hands slip off 
you halfway through last time.

279
00:16:56.010 --> 00:16:57.790
Ah, no, don't worry about it!

280
00:16:57.790 --> 00:16:59.520
I should be the one apologizing!

281
00:17:00.800 --> 00:17:05.240
This time, I've come with a spell that can 
teleport Your Highness, no contact needed.

282
00:17:05.240 --> 00:17:08.550
Oh, a new spell in so little time?

283
00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:10.400
You're not in the First Legion for nothing!

284
00:17:10.400 --> 00:17:11.530
Oh, please, no.

285
00:17:11.530 --> 00:17:12.620
A genius, you say?

286
00:17:12.620 --> 00:17:13.960
I didn't go that far.

287
00:17:13.960 --> 00:17:16.620
Ah, if you'll excuse me for a moment.

288
00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:21.270
Now then, Your Highness.

289
00:17:21.690 --> 00:17:24.940
I've cast a sleeping spell throughout 
the castle tonight as well.

290
00:17:24.940 --> 00:17:28.040
That said, let's act as 
silently as possible.

291
00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:31.850
How will we make our escape this time?

292
00:17:32.150 --> 00:17:33.660
Allow me to explain.

293
00:17:33.980 --> 00:17:36.410
My new spell, Entity Displacement.

294
00:17:36.810 --> 00:17:38.530
Entity Displacement?

295
00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:43.790
NOT TELEPORTED

296
00:17:38.740 --> 00:17:45.620
CHANTING

297
00:17:38.940 --> 00:17:41.400
This spell creates an 
expanding aura of mana,

298
00:17:41.400 --> 00:17:43.370
which teleports all matter within its range.

299
00:17:43.370 --> 00:17:45.670
Huh, that sure is a handy spell.

300
00:17:43.790 --> 00:17:45.620
TELEPORTED

301
00:17:46.100 --> 00:17:50.230
However, the drawback is that living things 
and objects can't travel at the same time,

302
00:17:50.230 --> 00:17:54.110
so your clothes and body end up 
being teleporting separately.

303
00:17:54.110 --> 00:17:54.730
Eh?

304
00:17:55.110 --> 00:17:57.000
Your clothes will be teleported first.

305
00:17:58.290 --> 00:17:59.020
Huh?

306
00:17:59.020 --> 00:17:59.690
Hold it right—

307
00:17:59.690 --> 00:18:01.300
O thou who dost seek the city.

308
00:18:01.300 --> 00:18:03.270
He's already in concentration mode!

309
00:18:01.670 --> 00:18:04.740
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

310
00:18:03.660 --> 00:18:06.390
Clothes and body separately, he says...

311
00:18:04.740 --> 00:18:06.460
Let my true form cross time and space,

312
00:18:06.460 --> 00:18:08.520
and serve as a brilliant guiding light.

313
00:18:08.520 --> 00:18:10.220
O thou who dost seek the city.

314
00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:13.710
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

315
00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:12.920
My clothes are starting to 
be teleported by themselves!

316
00:18:12.920 --> 00:18:13.690
If this keeps up...

317
00:18:13.690 --> 00:18:16.250
I'll end up buck naked!

318
00:18:16.740 --> 00:18:17.440
Heya.

319
00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:19.100
Wait, don't panic.

320
00:18:17.440 --> 00:18:21.590
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

321
00:18:19.100 --> 00:18:20.180
Calm down.

322
00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:21.730
Let's just calm down!

323
00:18:21.590 --> 00:18:23.620
Let my true form cross time and space,

324
00:18:22.340 --> 00:18:23.610
That's right.

325
00:18:23.610 --> 00:18:27.550
I'm the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion.

326
00:18:23.620 --> 00:18:25.890
and serve as a brilliant guiding light.

327
00:18:29.300 --> 00:18:32.440
I've faced all sorts of 
hardships in the past.

328
00:18:32.440 --> 00:18:37.010
In comparison, exposing my 
naked body is no big deal!

329
00:18:37.550 --> 00:18:40.670
I won't give in to the likes 
of being stripped naked!

330
00:18:42.810 --> 00:18:44.450
Wait, wait, wait, wait!

331
00:18:44.450 --> 00:18:46.710
Nope, nope, nope, nope, nope!

332
00:18:46.710 --> 00:18:48.660
O thou who dost seek the city.

333
00:18:46.710 --> 00:18:48.730
Stop, stop, stop!

334
00:18:48.660 --> 00:18:51.810
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

335
00:18:48.730 --> 00:18:50.850
Damn it, he's completely ignoring me!

336
00:18:50.850 --> 00:18:53.600
Seriously, how can he focus so intently?!

337
00:18:51.810 --> 00:18:53.600
Let my true form cross time and space,

338
