00:18:58.130 --> 00:19:01.620
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

343
00:18:59.190 --> 00:19:01.060
If he's concentrating this hard,

344
00:19:01.060 --> 00:19:04.730
I don't need to worry about 
being seen, even if I'm naked.

345
00:19:01.620 --> 00:19:03.590
Let my true form cross time and space,

346
00:19:03.590 --> 00:19:05.470
and serve as a brilliant guiding light.

347
00:19:05.470 --> 00:19:07.730
O thou who dost seek the city.

348
