No way, not happening!

361
00:19:29.310 --> 00:19:33.900
23rd
White Knight Cup

362
00:19:30.470 --> 00:19:33.690
<i>I'm left with no choice but 
to defeat Louch yet again!</i>

363
00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:38.480
