00:20:04.650 --> 00:20:06.930
<i>It doesn't count as a draw in real life!</i>

379
00:20:06.180 --> 00:20:06.930
Free my flesh from...

380
00:20:06.930 --> 00:20:09.220
23rd
White Knight Cup

381
00:20:07.240 --> 00:20:09.010
<i>I need to do something about this.</i>

382
00:20:09.710 --> 00:20:12.390
