00:20:27.130 --> 00:20:30.120
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

393
00:20:30.120 --> 00:20:31.870
Let my true form cross time and space,

394
00:20:31.870 --> 00:20:33.770
and serve as a brilliant guiding light.

395
00:20:33.770 --> 00:20:35.710
O thou who dost seek the city.

396
00:20:35.710 --> 00:20:38.630
Free my flesh from its 
armor, and behold my soul.

397
00:20:38.630 --> 00:20:40.780
Let my true form cross time and space,

398
00:20:39.250 --> 00:20:42.790
